[h3 id=4-1 
	"4-1
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Have to slow down a bit at the end to get a green guy off a platform but this a pretty much a run-past everything stage.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=4-2 
	"4-2
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"You can always see the floor but you frequently cannot see your ninja or enemies.  If you use the Game Genie code AAPA-CASG, you can never see the floor but you can always see your player and all enemies.  I did the first part without the code and the second part with it.  When I turned off the code, the movie doesn't desync.  (Note to be 100% clear:  No Game Genie codes are needed to play back this movie.)
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Boss4 
	"Boss 4
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"I kill him as fast I as I can but he's invincible most of the time.  Ninja magic doesn't speed things up any so I don't use it.  There's a bit of odd jockeying for position to get the last shots in as soon as possible.
	$LF
]p
