[h3 id=Level5 
	"Level 5
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Lots of running, very little fighting.  The sword may be slow but that works to my advantage here, as it damages a large and slightly spread out group roly poly guys.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Boss5 
	"Boss 5
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Another boss that's both invincible unless attacking and takes a long time to attack.  This boss is even immune to ninja magic most of the time.  Since the boss takes his merry time to attack, even if the ninjas die quickly, I spend most of the stage finding enteraining ways to kick ninjas.  I end the game with ninja magic--this saves a bunch of frames as activating the fatal ninja magic clinches the game, allowing me to quit the movie as soon as I release the button.
	$LF
]p
